---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Layout title="Bibleio">
  <main
    class="grid grid-cols-2 grid-rows-2 max-[1000px]:grid-rows-3 max-[1000px]:grid-cols-1 divide-x-[1px] divide-y-[1px] h-[150vh] max-[1000px]:h-[270vh] divide-black"
  >
    <div
      class="col-span-1 row-span-1 flex items-center justify-center flex-col gap-32 p-64 max-[1380px]:p-24 overflow-clip"
    >
      <h1
        class="leading-none text-[256px] font-lora font-normal max-[1700px]:text-[128px] max-[450px]:text-[96px]"
      >
        Bibleio
      </h1>
      <p class="body text-center">
        Useful tools to connect with the Bible, and to spread the gospel.
      </p>
      <div class="absolute bg-[#00A3FF] w-[30%] h-[25%] -z-10 blur-[192px]">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="col-span-1 min-[1000px]:row-span-2 grid grid-rows-2 divide-y-[1px] divide-black"
    >
      <a
        href="https://app.bibleio.com"
        class="p-64 max-[1000px]:p-24 flex justify-start items-end overflow-clip group"
      >
        <h1 class="h1">Bible App</h1>
        <Image
          src="/index/bible.svg"
          alt="Bible book"
          width={1024}
          height={1024}
          class="w-[423px] h-[354px] max-[1000px]:w-[211px] max-[1000px]:h-[177px] absolute -z-10 left-[77%] max-[1000px]:left-[60%] group-hover:-translate-y-24 duration-150 ease-out"
        />
      </a>
      <a
        href="/why-believe"
        class="p-64 max-[1000px]:p-24 flex justify-start items-end overflow-clip group"
      >
        <h1 class="h1">Why Believe?</h1>
        <Image
          src="/index/cross.svg"
          alt="Cross"
          width={1024}
          height={1024}
          class="w-[292px] h-[453px] max-[1000px]:w-[146px] max-[1000px]:h-[226px] absolute -z-10 left-[80%] max-[1000px]:left-[64%] group-hover:-translate-y-24 duration-150 ease-out"
        />
      </a>
    </div>
    <div
      class="col-span-1 row-span-1 grid grid-cols-2 max-[1000px]:grid-cols-1 max-[1000px]:grid-rows-2 divide-x-[1px] max-[1000px]:divide-y-[1px] max-[1000px]:h-[150%] divide-black"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col p-64 max-[1380px]:p-24 gap-24">
        <h1 class="h1">About</h1>
        <p class="body-paragraph">
          Bibleio is a product focused on spreading the gospel, and making the
          Bible accessible for everyone. I wanted to express God through my
          skills, and find a unique way to spread the gospel through a simple
          link. so I founded Bibleio. Bibleio is also very design focused, and I
          plan to make it unique. And Bibleio is 100% free and open-source.
        </p>
        <Button text="Source Code" link="https://github.com/bibleio" newTab />
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col p-64 max-[1380px]:p-24 gap-24">
        <h1 class="h1">Features & Plans</h1>
        <p class="body-paragraph">
          Bibleio is currently in alpha stages. Currently it can access the
          Bible, and you can format the text. I plan to add a "Why Believe?"
          page, search dialog, testimony sharing system, definition system,
          share system, bookmarks, a mobile app, a Discord bot, a Bible CLI, and
          a YouTube channel with helpful videos.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
